  ('dietitian-moex-01811', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關胸腺嘧啶核苷酸合成酶（thymidylate synthase）參與核苷酸（nucleotides）代謝之敘述，下列 何者正確？', '["胸腺嘧啶核苷酸合成酶（thymidylate synthase）可催化dTTP（deoxythymidine triphosphate）轉 變成dUTP（deoxyuridine triphosphate）", "胸腺嘧啶核苷酸合成酶（thymidylate synthase）之作用需要輔酶Q10（coenzyme Q10）作為輔酶", "磺醯尿素（sulfonylurea）可抑制胸腺嘧啶核苷酸合成酶（thymidylate synthase）作用，而作為 抗癌用藥", "胸腺嘧啶核苷酸合成酶（thymidylate synthase）之作用與四氫葉酸（tetrahydrofolate）代謝密切 相關"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce2dbd3ab2da", "answer_pdf_sha1": "00f73a9082c8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01812', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '抑制劑的結構與酵素專一性的受質結構很類似時，可與酵素活性中心結合，在提高受質濃度時不 影響最大反應速率（V ），Michaelis常數（Km）也會增加。請問此屬何種類型酵素抑制劑？ max', '["競爭型抑制劑（competitive inhibition）", "異位性抑制劑（allosteric inhibition）", "不競爭型抑制劑（uncompetitive inhibition）", "非競爭型抑制劑（noncompetitive inhibition）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce2dbd3ab2da", "answer_pdf_sha1": "00f73a9082c8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
